		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I played my game after several months off, and I thought &quot;wow, this scrolls too fast&quot;.<br /><br />These Game Genie codes will slow the right scrolling by 20%. Which feels a little better.<br /><br />YLXOTLLK + YLUPZLAK.<br /><br />However, this makes 1 jump in level 5 quite a bit harder to make. (not available in the demo).<br /><br />By the way. I have about 10 copies of this game left on cartridge. If anyone wants a copy ($) let me know. Thanks. Soon, I might auction the rest of the games off.

		

